title: Grateful Dead Live at Hartford Civic Center on 1983-10-15
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab 2496 > R8Brain SRC > Wavelab (adding 16-bit patches) > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 tagged. Transferred by Andrew F. 06/2016
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Dire Wolf, Minglewood Blues, Brown Eyed Women, Wang Dang Doodle, Big Railroad Blues, Let It Grow-> Day Job

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Drums-> Saint Stephen-> Throwing Stones-> One More Saturday Night, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text: Tops So many outstanding recordings for this show.  This is one of the top captures, thanks for sharing.
